
'''Lina Mukashyaka Higiro''' ni umucuruzikazi wo mu [[Rwanda]] kandi yabaye umuyobozi mukuru wa Banki ya NCBA mu Rwanda kuva muri Nyakanga 2018<ref>https://en.igihe.com/news/article/lina-higiro-among-top-3-seasoned-women-shaping-east-africa-s-banking-financial</ref>. <ref name="1R">http://www.newtimes.co.rw/business/cba-bank-rwanda-new-ceo</ref> mbere yuko ahabwa inshingano, kuva muri Nyakanga 2016, yabaye umuyobozi mukuru wa AB Bank Rwanda . Muri uru ruhare, yagenzuye imikorere ya banki, amabanki y’ubucuruzi, iterambere ry’ubucuruzi n’imari ya digitale<ref>https://kenyanwallstreet.com/angaza-awards-top-10-finalists-lina-higiro/</ref><ref name="2R">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xgHL3Zf6Zvk</ref>.   Mbere yibyo, Higiro yari Umuyobozi w’Ingamba, Igenamigambi n’Ubucuruzi muri  I&amp;amp;M Banki , kandi mbere yaho yakoraga muri Guaranty Trust Bank (icyo gihe yari Fina Bank), nk'umuyobozi wa Banki , kuva 2007 kugeza 2011. <ref name="1R" />

== Amavu n'amavuko ==
Yize muri kaminuza ya  North-West University, muri Afurika yepfo, arangizanya impamyabumenyi y’ubucuruzi <ref>https://rw.ncbagroup.com/meet-the-team/</ref><ref name="1R" />. Nyuma, yabonye Master of Business Administration yakuye muri kaminuza ya Liverpool mu [[Bwongereza]] <ref name=":0">https://igihe.com/abantu/biographies/article/yatangiye-akora-mu-mw-isomero-none-ni-umwe-mu</ref>.  Afite kandi icyemezo mu bucuruzi n’itumanaho ry’amasosiyete, cyatanzwe na kaminuza ya Ryerson, i Toronto, muri [[Kanada]]<ref name=":0" />.

